sub_title: Moving the needle in insurtech business | Product Owner @ Insify
summary:
I like to think about myself as an enthusiastic and responsible individual with an outgoing personality who happily lead the way on difficult paths.

I am an experienced business consultant with a demonstrated history of working in the computer software and banking industry. I believe that digitalization and technology can move the world forward, and I would like to be a part of it.

Everything you do right now ripples outward and affects everyone. Your posture can shine your heart or transmit anxiety. Your breath can radiate love or muddy the room in depression. Your glance can awaken joy. Your words can inspire freedom. Your every act can open hearts and minds.
- David Deida
